project_detailed.project_features_description: The Pricelist Upload feature allows data to be uploaded through an Excel file and uses a chunking method for the upload process. During the development of this feature, there are stages for uploading and periodic checking. The API for checking is called at 10-second intervals, and once the process is complete, the user is redirected to the summary view.
The Pricelist Display feature provides a way to display the data that has been uploaded. Additionally, users can correct any mistakes by updating the uploaded data through this feature.
